This paper deals with secure compilation, which is a topic in computer security (cs.CR). It also involves formal methods and logic (cs.LO), programming languages (cs.PL), software engineering (cs.SE), and formal verification (cs.FL). The abstract mentions trace properties, hyperproperties, and relational hyperproperties, which are all related to program behavior and semantics, further supporting the likelihood of these sub-categories.
